Пользователи по отделам.sql:
SELECT 
    eq_departments.name AS department_name,
    equsers.firstname,
    equsers.surname,
    equsers.email
FROM 
    equsers
JOIN 
    eq_departments ON equsers.department = eq_departments.id
WHERE 
    equsers.deleted = FALSE AND eq_departments.deleted = FALSE;
